==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: auto-
<hw>au"to-</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <ety>[Gr. <?/ self.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>A combining form, with the meaning of <xex>self</xex>, <xex>one's
self</xex>, <xex>one's own</xex>, <xex>itself</xex>, <xex>its
own</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>a prefix with the meaning of <xex>self-moving</xex>,
<xex>self-propelling</xex>; <as>as, an <ex>auto</ex>car, an
<ex>auto</ex>carriage, an <ex>auto</ex>truck, etc.</as>, an automobile
car, carriage, truck, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>autobahn</ent>⟦br⟧
